{"UNSUBSTANTIAL":[{"def":"Lacking in matter or substance; visionary; chimerical.","pos":""}],"UNSUBSTANTIALIZE":[{"def":"To make unsubstantial.","pos":""}],"UNSUBSTANTIATION":[{"def":"A divesting of substantiality.","pos":""}],"UNSUCCEEDABLE":[{"def":"Not able or likely to succeed.","pos":""}],"UNSUCCESS":[{"def":"Want of success; failure; misfortune.","pos":""}],"UNSUCCESSFUL":[{"def":"Not successful; not producing the desired event; not fortunate; meeting with, or resulting in, failure; unlucky; unhappy.","pos":""}],"UNSUFFERING":[{"def":"Inability or incapability of enduring, or of being endured.","pos":""}],"UNSUIT":[{"def":"Not to suit; to be unfit for.","pos":""}],"UNSUPPORTABLE":[{"def":"Insupportable; unendurable.","pos":""}],"UNSURED":[{"def":"Thy now unsured assurance to the crown.","pos":""}],"UNSURETY":[{"def":"Want of surety; uncertainty; insecurity; doubt.","pos":""}],"UNSURMOUNTABLE":[{"def":"Un`sur*mount\"a*ble, a.","pos":""}],"UNSUSPICION":[{"def":"The quality or state of being unsuspecting.","pos":""}]}